description: Live in the heart of the Seaport at Pier 4 in this sunny 1 bedroom, 1.5 bath home with gorgeous water views from every room. This stunning open layout luxury condo with private balcony, open floor plan, and top-of-the-line finishes is a true oasis in the city. Fabuous chef’s kitchen has custom cabinetry, Gaggenau appliances, and a waterfall marble kitchen island. Primary bedroom accommodates a king bed and features a walk-in closet; en suite marble bath boasts a massive shower, double vanity & full linen closet.  Gorgeous Italian walnut floors throughout, W/D, and bountiful storage. One garage parking space included. This boutique building of just 106 homes, offers generous amenities: 24-hour concierge, doorman, common terrace with fire pit and grill, resident lounge, full gym, & golf simulator. Located in the middle of the Seaport’s vibrant shopping, dining & nightlife adjacent to the ICA Boston.
